Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是西条拓巳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.26,0:01:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑名和梢梢跟我三个人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.12,0:01:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对将giga-lo-maniacs这一力量作不法用途的企业
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NOZOMI科技进行了袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.13,0:01:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这一计划被社长野吕濑玄一看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野吕濑也是giga-lo-maniacs
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.58,0:01:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他利用这一力量折磨着濑名和梢梢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.58,0:01:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且想连我也一并铲除
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在此时  奇迹发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.09,0:02:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑来救我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过费尽艰辛所打倒的野吕濑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.62,0:02:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是冒牌货
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉哦  让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我涩谷警署的判
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是楠优爱小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.44,0:02:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.56,0:02:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是NewGene第一个案件「集体跳楼」其中一个受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楠美爱的双胞胎姐姐  没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.58,0:02:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优爱她似乎独自一人调查着NewGene事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了得知美爱究竟发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.18,0:02:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后她查到了某一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是西条拓巳君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.18,0:03:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟我详细说下么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…虽然想这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过请稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈  第六件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NewGene第六起事件发生了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第六起事件？  怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害者三人身体均被切断
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.53,0:03:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各人的上半身和下半身被调转并鱼丝再拼起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸体上分别有「D」「Q」「N」模样的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.29,0:03:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那帮家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.69,0:03:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前来找我麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是将军  是他在挑衅我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点  肯定只是巧合啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.31,0:04:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  我肚子饿了  要不要去哪里吃饭？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了一间物美价廉的店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧  我被这样的事情烦透了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  那边就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这边很可能找到了重要的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你准备打开潘多拉的盒子么  前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.96,0:04:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,37.1度  有点烧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的头像被针插般痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  又来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这只是药的副作用而已  别担心  很快就能好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前也有过这样的症状
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算现在被如何对待我也毫不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.82,0:04:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我挺过了那个神罚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这呆茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军为何会盯上我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.11,0:05:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我以前经常使用的句子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小学也写过这样的作文
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我写了些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个呆茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点莫名其妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ir2？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个公式  跟将军的发言一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的思考被他窥视了么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…将军？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  是七海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.35,0:06:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…救…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶作剧么  烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优爱有听过你的学校有变戏法很厉害的女生么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,譬如从空无一物的地方将剑变出来之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道她的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是岸本绫濑同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她从空无一物的地方将剑变出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到的是叫苍井濑名的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.18,0:06:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在涩谷到处都有流传有人目击了苍井挥舞着大剑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实还有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时侯岸本同学  分裂成两个了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.19,0:07:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已确认岸本绫濑和苍井濑名都和西条拓巳有过接触
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西条君…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个少年身边尽是发生一些离奇的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  优爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.67,0:07:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的手提包上挂着的是现在在年轻人中很流行的呱呱青蛙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能帮我去买个回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呱呱…啥来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呱呱青蛙  在涩谷有几间专卖店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论哪间专卖店在周五都大排长龙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周五…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每周五会有新的品种发售
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小判
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.47,0:07:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得重力异常值是每逢周末而上升的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去刺探一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓  阿拓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:07:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岸本的病房是哪间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是门诊部  住院部是在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗  你知道得还挺详细啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿大  你认真点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿大你提议说一起来探病的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只找了阿拓而已  你是擅自跟来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这回事么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一下洗手间  你们先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她跑哪去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉齐奥尔传奇？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似是科幻小说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和岸本谈恋爱的话  也要配合她这样的爱好么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑已经能下床走动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来梨深那家伙  知道病房在这里么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是个大笨蛋  不会想到跟我们一样去问路的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去找她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:09:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓  你和岸本交往的事  果然是谣言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有梨深在你就像寂寞得要死一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去找下层
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.62,0:09:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去上层
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢  我有一种不应该待在这里的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别…看我！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.85,0:09:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又被将军窥视思考了吗  我要回家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神光救赎  神光救赎  神光救赎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓拓原来是个宅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.52,0:10:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西条拓巳绝非常人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人协助他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「那视线是谁的视线」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然拓拓就是「那视线是谁的视线」的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梢梢太感动了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ir2？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名名？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是怎么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  阿拓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.51,0:10:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你脸色不太好哦  嘛  虽然平时也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到梨深和岸本了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.03,0:11:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们两个是不是有啥恩怨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  刚刚的我们当作没看见好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  岸本同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岸本同学  你穿睡衣也很可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  阿拓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.08,0:11:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的伤势如何  看来你似乎好了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岸本同学  你有看小说么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有在看格拉齐奥尔传奇…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓巳  你是格拉齐奥尔七骑士其中一人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的邪心非常强大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你那黑骑士的资质是不可否认的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在所受到的痛苦全是神罚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是伟大意志给予的考验
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你顺利通过这些考验的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能召唤Di-Sword
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能把它握在手中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪心的黑色大蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吞噬一切崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉碎邪心王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.03,0:12:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既是同质又是异质的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够打倒格拉齐奥尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.78,0:12:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我已经做不出任何反应了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.78,0:12:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三住君  就算你留下我一个人也
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你创造出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时的花坛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是giga-lo-maniacs啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,giga-lo什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.86,0:12:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是giga-lo-maniacs
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是苍井濑名告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  是她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也是格拉齐奥尔的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.55,0:12:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  我不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没有Di-Sword
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战胜神罚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一来就能召唤剑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神罚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.37,0:13:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身心负荷的爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.44,0:13:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心门的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是  身心的拷问
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经在疗养院里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水滴垂直下落的速度是以每5秒为间隔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连续两周处于那种状态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我身心处于崩溃临界的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了伟大意志的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于能召唤出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.15,0:13:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是神罚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要获得击败邪心王的力量的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:13:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就需要纯粹的邪心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.28,0:14:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道就是说要让我再承受更多的痛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.23,0:14:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都是天启
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七名其实应该都已经聚集在涩谷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.03,0:14:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就是等待全员的觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点的话世界就会被格拉齐奥尔所毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.97,0:14:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我不认识医院的路  然后就一直在绕圈子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们见到岸本同学了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.38,0:14:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对岸本已经无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种电波语  我可没办法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一点事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是恶作剧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我适可而止一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.89,0:14:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:14:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.95,0:15:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不到周末的话就没什么客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  从周五到周日人满为患
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  只有在新作发售的周末
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在周末啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.14,0:15:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是明天要发售的蚰蜒青蛙新作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…应该是呱呱青蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.71,0:15:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有限公司shinko
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.71,0:15:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}注：和「神光」发音一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果刚才的电话不是恶作剧的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓  你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.39,0:15:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才开始就怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想先回老家一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.35,0:15:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  想和梨深一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:15:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你画的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑名为什么会有那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  所以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓拓快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.39,0:16:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么濑名会攻击我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨深
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  原来咲畑同学也是giga-lo-maniacs
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要逼迫阿拓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那个男人做了些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把Ir2这个公式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.74,0:16:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果让阿拓觉醒的话就会有更大的麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前我会把他灭掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.22,0:17:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.51,0:17:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能把你的母亲作为了祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的母亲  所以实验得到了出色的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你母亲派上用场了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.97,0:17:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于报了母亲的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  别随便碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你所期望的妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你看到了痛苦的回忆  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.17,0:18:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我别无他法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨深好像知道些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲咲  已经结束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想把名名{\fnsimhei\fs29}○○{\r}的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.21,0:18:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梢梢我可不会放过你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本就不打算对苍井同学出手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她能从阿拓面前消失的话
